|       |                           | Tier names, monthly price, bullet perks                          | Table or CSV (`tier,price,perk1,perk2…`)                    | `/data/tiers.csv`                 | ✓ | ✓ |
|       |                           | Fund description & risk disclaimer                               | Paragraph(s) of legal‑approved text                         | `/content/fund.md`                | ✓ | ✓ |
|       |                           | FAQs (Q\&A)                                                      | Markdown list                                               | `/content/faq.md`                 | ✓ | ✓ |
|       |                           | Testimonials (optional)                                          | Name, quote, photo                                          | `/content/testimonials.yaml`      | ✓ | ✓ |
| **3** | **Legal**                 | Terms of Service & Privacy Policy                                | Word/Google Doc or Markdown                                 | `/legal/`                         | ✓ | ✓ |
|       |                           | Investment risk disclosure                                       | Final text vetted by counsel                                | `/legal/risk.md`                  | ✓ | ✓ |
| **4** | **Technical Credentials** | Domain registrar / DNS access                                    | Login or delegated token                                    | **Secure vault**                  | ✓ | ✓ |
|       |                           | Hosting / Git repo access                                        | GitHub org invite or cPanel creds                           | **Secure vault**                  | ✓ | ✓ |
|       |                           | Stripe account (test & live keys)                                | `pk_` and `sk_` keys, web‑hook secret                       | `.env.staging`, `.env.production` |   | ✓ |
|       |                           | PayPal REST creds (if used)                                      | Client ID + Secret                                          | `.env*`                           |   | ✓ |
|       |                           | Email/SMS provider API keys (Sendgrid, Twilio)                   | Key string + verified sender domains                        | `.env*`                           |   | ✓ |
|       |                           | Brokerage / market‑data API creds                                | API secret; rate‑limit info                                 | `.env*`                           |   | ✓ |
